songs.title: Ain’t No Joke

Shit ain't no joke
All my niggas tote poles
We got them choppers
Fuck niggas get low
Lowerin' rounds, snipe a nigga off his toes
I'm on the block with the guys, we on go
Shit ain't no joke

[Verse]
If you out here actin' bad, bitch you gettin' whacked
Your wig gettin' split and your skull gettin' cracked
Bitch you know I'm trigger happy, don't know how to act
And my niggas doin' numbers like we sending fax
Bitch I ain't with that talkin', boy you gettin' clapped
You got them screws in your ear, bitch you gettin' jacked
My bitch ain't with that talkin' but her name is Chat
Bitch we bustin' caps, like backpacks we stay strapped
Nigga fuck the opps, I'm in traffic, I'm poured up
Got L's, all my niggas throwed off
Bitch you say you on the map, you gettin' knocked off
My kindergarten niggas blow your top off
I leave your whole shirt red like you spilled hot sauce
Your bitch knock me down like some dominos
Adios, bitch I'm 'bout my nachos
My niggas ringing bells like we sell tacos
